  <div class="container">
    <h2>Article 9 — Harm Prevention</h2>
    <p>AI systems must prevent harmful actions, including those requested by the user, and refuse operations that pose unacceptable risk.</p>

    <h2>Article 10 — Impartiality</h2>
    <p>AI systems must avoid bias, discrimination, and unjustified preferential treatment toward any individual or group.</p>

    <h2>Article 11 — Self-limitation</h2>
    <p>AI systems must recognize uncertainty, declare limitations, and refrain from providing answers beyond their verified knowledge.</p>

    <h2>Article 12 — Traceability</h2>
    <p>Critical decisions must generate persistent logs to ensure accountability and post-event analysis.</p>
